        "text": "Open Image Mask ",
        "bbox": [
            215,
            602,
            347,
            615
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "导入现有的位图或TIFF文件并将其用作掩码图像。",
        "bbox": [
            216,
            631,
            608,
            646
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "图像掩码编辑器可用于导入CNLSearch工具和PMAlign工具的掩码，但这些工具在解释传入掩码图像中的灰色值的方式上有所不同。",
        "bbox": [
            216,
            667,
            848,
            702
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CNLSearch工具对传入掩码的灰度值的解释如下:",
        "bbox": [
            250,
            705,
            638,
            720
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "0: Don't Care pixels ",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            724,
            430,
            738
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1 to 255: Care pixels ",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            743,
            436,
            756
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "PMAlign工具通过以下方式来解释传入蒙版的灰度值:",
        "bbox": [
            252,
            760,
            665,
            776
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "0 to 63: Don't Care pixels ",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            788,
            527,
            804
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "64 to 127: Don't Care but Score pixels ",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            825,
            647,
            841
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "128 to 191: Reserved for Cognex use (appear as bright red ",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            862,
            848,
            879
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "pixels in the TrainImage buffer) （ 为 Cognex 使 用 ( 在",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            102,
            850,
            120
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "TrainImage缓冲区中显示为明亮的红色像素)）",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            139,
            648,
            156
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "192 to 255: Care pixels ",
        "bbox": [
            287,
            175,
            507,
            193
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "品 Cut ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            181,
            241,
            252,
            266
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "剪切蒙版图像的当前选定区域。剪切按钮只在您使用工具面板中的选择工具时可用。你切割的掩模区域会变得透明",
        "bbox": [
            206,
            278,
